{"tid":2447516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸32家中企受損仍不撤僑 外交部：中國人自我防範","createTime":"2021-03-15T08:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T03:23:26.000Z","uid":337052,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"3c36b3e2bc65594d5bcd25928abfd95bfa089095","tid":2447516,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國是否安排從緬甸撤僑？外交部回應</span></strong><br />\n來源：環球時報-環球網<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-15 16:17<br />\n<br />\n【環球時報-環球網報導記者張卉】中國駐緬甸大使館剛剛向環球時報-環球網記者證實，截至15日中午，<span class=\"red\">14日發生的緬甸仰光萊達雅工業區多家中資工廠遭不法分​​子打砸事件共造成32家中資工廠受損，兩名中國員工受傷，無人死亡。據不完全統計，財產損失2.4億人民幣。</span>在15日中國外交部例行記者會上，有媒體詢問發言人中國是否會安排撤僑？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/files/imageDir/8dc543ad5f6f998f9cf5e7379be2d075u5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Ffiles%2FimageDir%2F8dc543ad5f6f998f9cf5e7379be2d075u5.jpg&h=0a6a1e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對此，中國外交部發言人趙立堅表示，關於緬甸局勢，我們希望緬甸各方保持冷靜克制，從緬甸人民的根本利益出發，堅持通過對話協商，在憲法和法律框架下解決矛盾分歧，繼續推進國內民主轉型進程。當務之急是防止發生新的流血衝突，盡快實現局勢緩和降溫。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅說，關於緬甸中資企業遭打砸搶事件，這次事件性質十分惡劣，事件發生後，中國駐緬甸使館第一時間同緬甸中國企業商會和相關企業取得了聯繫，迅速要求當地警方採取有力措施，保障中資企業及人員安全。緬方已經向涉事地區增派警力和消防力量，加強現場治安處置。中方將繼續敦促緬方採取切實措施，制止一切暴力行為，依法查處相關肇事者，確保在緬中資企業和人員的生命和財產安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/files/imageDir/7bc26076b0a80de5a832dd7c006e5b5au5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Ffiles%2FimageDir%2F7bc26076b0a80de5a832dd7c006e5b5au5.jpg&h=7da0098c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當地時間3月14日13時50分許，緬甸仰光蘭達亞工業區兩家服裝廠遭遇縱火。圖源 央視新聞<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅稱，我想強調中緬經貿合作始終基於互利共贏原則，有利於緬甸經濟社會發展，惠及緬甸當地民眾。這些不法分子的行為不符合緬甸和緬甸人民的利益。<span class=\"red\">我們呼籲緬甸民眾合法表達訴求，不被煽動和利用，避免損害中緬友好合作。</span><br />\n<br />\n關於中方是否考慮撤僑的問題，趙立堅說，中方密切關注緬甸局勢的發展，對中方機構和人員安全受到影響，非常關切。中方希望緬方採取切實措施，保護在緬中國公民的安全，堅決避免類似事件再次發生。<span class=\"red\"> &ldquo;同時我們提醒在緬中國公民提高安全防範意識，加強自身防範措施&rdquo;</span>，趙立堅說。<br />\n<br />\n舉報責編：魏少璞"},{"pid":"935dc2f44d0baabf4771e117aa8d62eab01ad7d7","tid":2447516,"uid":5191,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"吳驚出現未"},{"pid":"309ddca9b71b12a00a7a7e89d9246984ab105d12","tid":2447516,"uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"935dc2f44d0baabf4771e117aa8d62eab01ad7d7","tid":2447516,"uid":5191,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"吳驚出現未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"戰狼=站郎"},{"pid":"38d2b2df090c8e0b21ce49d31050e0d00c0f2a1a","tid":2447516,"uid":35814,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/09152834/fj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F09152834%2Ffj1.jpg&h=5330901f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7484b9c7953b2b88f30c3adb3271e51200b06368","tid":2447516,"uid":50931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16617f48a0583644453004748c5c676ae165c2b5","tid":2447516,"uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">緬甸反中情緒爆發！ 民眾破壞中資工廠 揚言抵制中國商品</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/15/phpc20ah6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F15%2Fphpc20ah6.jpg&h=b32a2968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緬甸民眾上街呼籲中國不要支持軍政府。緬甸反中情緒爆發，14日有民眾進入中資工廠破壞。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n2021/03/15 06:24<br />\n首次上稿 00:28<br />\n更新時間 06:24<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕緬甸軍政府政變，該國動盪不安，該國民眾更懷疑中國暗中幫助緬甸軍隊，提高反中情緒，昨天（14日）爆發不滿，民眾持鐵棍、斧頭進入大城仰光2間中資工廠破壞，宣洩不滿。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，中國數次被媒體指涉暗助緬甸軍政府，緬甸民眾懷疑中國立場，湧現反中浪潮，今天不滿中國的民眾騎機車，帶著鐵棍、斧頭和石油到仰光的中資衣服工廠進行破壞。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">憤怒的緬甸民眾也揚言會抵制中國產品</span>，甚至有抗議領袖人士認為，應該呼籲印度企業到緬甸拓展市場，指出就算價錢較高，緬甸民眾不支持中國，轉支持印度產品。<br />\n<br />\n仰光的反軍政府抗議中，也出現民眾手持<span class=\"red\">「緬甸政變，中國製造」</span>的標語，部分民眾呼喊<span class=\"red\">「燒掉中國天然氣管線」</span>的口號。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">曼德勒一條總長770公里連通道中國的油氣管線，過去被中國宣揚為「互惠合作」的象徵，如今因中國疑暗助緬甸軍政府，成為緬甸反中情緒的目標。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3466839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3466839&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDj44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=e998fa9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3466839&h=c7f78434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3466839</a>"},{"pid":"a3ddbef81c5deb86a2615a4475438b9cd0eb1533","tid":2447516,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQp5L6C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQp5L6C.gif&h=ccb3ed2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96992a663e8a44a414f91f06c4fa825c4d2289f1","tid":2447516,"uid":2054,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"中國人條命賤過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十幾億死咗咪其他踩住你上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9719429007dcf4ef5488d9b0322dc9a5bbf0b6e5","tid":2447516,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:55:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國駐緬使館：打砸事件造成32家中資工廠受損，兩中國員工受傷，財產損失約2.4億元</span></strong><br />\n來源：環球時報-環球網<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-15 14:04<br />\n<br />\n【環球時報-環球網報導】中國駐緬甸大使館剛剛向環球時報-環球網記者證實，截至15日中午，14日發生的緬甸仰光萊達雅工業區發生多家中資工廠遭不法分​​子打砸事件共造成32家中資工廠受損，兩名中國員工受傷，無人死亡。據不完全統計，財產損失2.4億人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n據此前媒體報導，自當地時間3月14日下午開始至傍晚，緬甸仰光多個工業區的十多家工廠遭遇縱火和打砸，涉及企業多數為中資企業或中緬合資企業，其中以服裝加工廠、服裝輔料廠和配套設備廠為主。縱火者大多騎著摩托車，帶有鐵棍、斧子和汽油桶，衝進工廠以後先是打砸和恐嚇工廠值班人員，之後便開始縱火。<br />\n<br />\n14日，中國駐緬甸使館發言人就在緬中資企業遭打砸搶燒發表談話稱，3月14日下午，緬甸仰光萊達雅工業區多家中資工廠遭不法分​​子打砸搶燒，多名中方人員受傷，有員工一度被困。中國駐緬甸使館第一時間同緬甸中國企業商會和相關企業取得聯繫，迅速要求當地警方採取有力措施，保障中資企業及人員安全。使館還再次向中國在緬企業和人員發出安全提示。使館發言人還表示，這次打砸搶燒事件性質十分惡劣。中方要求緬方採取進一步有效措施，制止一切暴力行為，依法查處相關肇事者，確保在緬中國企業和人員的生命和財產安全。我們呼籲緬甸民眾合法表達訴求，不被煽動和利用，破壞中緬友好合作。<br />\n<br />\n舉報責編：王怡"},{"pid":"becdb9e6e06ca582bf24ae778bba0bc888cb8ea7","tid":2447516,"uid":179729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"如果真係燒油氣管，一定好撚震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35128e525edb16788ff9e4ae93a92409ee21c39","tid":2447516,"uid":337052,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"becdb9e6e06ca582bf24ae778bba0bc888cb8ea7","tid":2447516,"uid":179729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"如果真係燒油氣管，一定好撚震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2021/03/12/4d234ce26f51b2d33006bece69b3bbcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2021%2F03%2F12%2F4d234ce26f51b2d33006bece69b3bbcb.jpg&h=afaa6ab2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec56039cb7f10b225a5fdba88b73571010579b42","tid":2447516,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f35128e525edb16788ff9e4ae93a92409ee21c39","tid":2447516,"uid":337052,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"becdb9e6e06ca582bf24ae778bba0bc888cb8ea7","tid":2447516,"uid":179729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"如果真係燒油氣管，一定好撚震撼<img src=\"/assets/